   <description>
      <short>
         <en>Gapp Essentials is a mandatory plugin to enable additional features on Gapp, a GLPI mobile app.</en>
      </short>
      <long>
         <en>
            Gapp Essentials is a mandatory plugin that enables advanced functionality in Gapp, the mobile application for GLPI. 
            Beginning with Gapp 2, the Gapp Essentials plugin has become a prerequisite for the app's operation.
            We strongly recommend updating GLPI to safeguard against security vulnerabilities. 
            The versions currently supported are: 11.0.0 and above 
            Currently enables: 
            -Access to ticket documents 
            -Plugins list to Self-service users 
            -Max. uploadable file size 
            -Allowed filetypes 
            -Download file size
         </en>
      </long>
   </description>
